Cristine Rose https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cristine_Rose 0 Cristine Sue Rose (born January 31, 1951) is an American actress. She has also been credited as Christine Rose. She is best known for her role as Angela Petrelli on the hit NBC science fiction drama Heroes. Cristine_Sue_Rose ( born January_31_,_1951 ) is an_American_actress .
